data.description: Welcome to this exquisite colonial in the sought-after Bel Air, Vineyard Oak North neighborhood, offering an impressive blend of sophistication and comfort. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths across 4800+ finished square feet, this residence is a true haven of luxury.As you step through the grand 2-story foyer, you are greeted by the warmth of a stone fireplace in the family room, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream with stainless steel appliances, along with granite countertops, a stylish backsplash, a spacious island, and an adjoining sunroom that fills the space with natural light.Working from home is a pleasure in the well-appointed study with French doors, providing a quiet and elegant space. The open finished basement adds an extra dimension to the home, complete with a wet bar, an additional bedroom, and a full bath.The serene backyard is a private retreat, offering a built-in stone fireplace and a hardscape patio, providing ample space for outdoor entertaining or quiet relaxation. The landscaping complements the ambiance, creating a perfect balance between beauty and tranquility.Recent updates include new carpeting upstairs, new flooring in the master closet, and in laundry room. Also, the upstairs hall bath with new ceramic tiles, lighting, and a new vanity in 2023. New HVAC system in 2022.The powder room received a stylish makeover in 2021, featuring new paint, a modern vanity, and updated lighting fixtures. Throughout the home, light fixtures have been updated as well.This Colonial gem not only offers a luxurious living experience but also presents a meticulously maintained and thoughtfully updated residence. Schedule your private tour to experience the epitome of Bel Air living in this stunning home.
